title: Das Duell um die Geld
overview: Joko and Klaas go all-in and invite good friends to a "duel for the money" for the money. Quiz meets poker at the big game night. Knowledge meets bluffing. Absolute cluelessness meets big winnings. In keeping with the occasion quiz questions are posed in a stylish ambience and the correct The correct answer is then played at the gaming table. Who can shine with knowledge shine? Who can bankrupt themselves? Who will bluff their way to victory?
